so we gonna make a API for many brand of guitar.

For Database:
1. brands: id, brand_name, country, created_at, updated_at
2. body_shapes: id, shape_name, created_at, updated_at
3. product: id, brand_id, shape_id, model_name, created_at, updated_at
4. specifications: id, product_id, body_material, neck_material, fretboard_material, bridge_type, pickup_config, scale_length, created_at, updated_at

relations:
1. Brands ke Product (1:N)
2. Body Shapes ke Product (1:N)
3. Product ke Specifications (1:1)


folder management: https://blog.anikety.com/go-backend-project-structure